summary: Completed comprehensive end-to-end testing of Moltbot deployment app. All features working correctly including setup page UI, provider selection, API key input, validation, loading states, and successful integration with Moltbot Control UI.
passed_tests: Backend: Root API endpoint returns correct response
Backend: GET /api/moltbot/status returns running status correctly
Backend: POST /api/moltbot/start validates provider (rejects invalid providers)
Backend: POST /api/moltbot/start validates API key length (rejects short keys)
Backend: POST /api/moltbot/start successfully starts Moltbot gateway
Backend: Legacy status endpoints (POST/GET /api/status) working
Backend: Proxy endpoint /api/moltbot/ui/ successfully proxies to Moltbot Control UI
Frontend: Setup page loads with dark theme (#0f0f10 background)
Frontend: Lobster emoji (ðŸ¦ž) displayed in header
Frontend: Provider select dropdown works with Anthropic and OpenAI options
Frontend: API key input field with password masking by default
Frontend: Show/hide toggle button reveals/hides API key
Frontend: Start button correctly disabled when provider or API key is empty
Frontend: Start button enabled when both provider and API key are filled
Frontend: API key placeholder changes based on provider (sk-ant-... for Anthropic, sk-... for OpenAI)
Frontend: Documentation link points to correct URL (https://docs.molt.bot/web/control-ui)
Frontend: Help link points to GitHub (https://github.com/moltbot/moltbot)
Integration: Status check runs on page load
Integration: 'Moltbot is running' status card appears when already running
Integration: 'Open Control UI' button redirects to /api/moltbot/ui/
Integration: Start button click triggers loading state with progress bar
Integration: Loading status text updates during startup (Validating configuration, Starting...)
Integration: Toast notification 'Moltbot is already running!' appears when appropriate
Integration: Successful redirect to Moltbot Control UI after startup
Integration: Moltbot Control UI loads correctly via proxy
